{"tid":659230,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"卡斯拿斯：我冇掛住皇馬","createTime":"2018-05-09T15:45:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-11T08:33:37.000Z","uid":54373,"like":28,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"b5d448a5b14c034954fe07811ecdba315f7161c7","tid":659230,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T15:45:03.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=wapzj4paykHaBJyKCXJ%2FodU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=2ab060a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】在2015年離開皇家馬德里的傳奇門將卡斯拿斯十分絕情，坦言<span style=\"color: red;\">毫無想念這家母會</span>。<br />\n<br />\n「我沒有想念皇家馬德里，他們是你生命中的其中一個階段，而你一定要向前走。」卡斯拿斯（Iker Casillas）當年離開皇馬前，長時間坐冷板，可說是不歡而散。「皇馬給予我所有，我踢大賽、贏冠軍、為國家隊出戰。我永遠都會感謝皇馬，而且永遠都是他們的球迷。」<br />\n<br />\n在2015年加盟波圖後，聖卡斯今季終於嘗到葡超冠軍的滋味：「當你老去，捧盃是很重要的，因為這給予你動力。要是你長時間未能贏得冠軍，你會變得沮喪。於我來說，我想多踢1年，我只會作短期計劃，享受當下。」36歲的他跟波圖的合約在季後就完結，但仍未續約。"},{"pid":"6be1682435f40569c17d1bb4f0cbfa503d0d833f","tid":659230,"uid":35547,"like":39,"dislike":6,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T15:48:24.000Z","msg":"但王騎無時無刻都諗住皇馬"},{"pid":"4629ef4d75d7d32814653f55ef0493bfeb576d2d","tid":659230,"uid":45772,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6be1682435f40569c17d1bb4f0cbfa503d0d833f","tid":659230,"uid":35547,"like":39,"dislike":6,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T15:48:24.000Z","msg":"但王騎無時無刻都諗住皇馬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T15:50:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a7aef4a0eba71a168cb37ef5d963745ed6bf8af","tid":659230,"uid":42734,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T15:54:56.000Z","msg":"咁撚樣對個功臣，係人都唔掛"},{"pid":"ccc276d127c3dadfb8a97e82006c368c19f02c79","tid":659230,"uid":22913,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T15:57:45.000Z","msg":"自己攞黎